Установка nginx

$ mkdir opt
$ cd ./opt
$ sudo mkdir nginx
$ cd nginx/
$ sudo chmod 777 .
$ curl -L http://nginx.org/packages/ubuntu/pool/nginx/n/nginx/nginx_1.18.0-1~focal_amd64.deb -O
скачалось, смотрим содержимое
$ dpkg -c nginx_1.18.0-1~focal_amd64.deb
Установка пакета
$ sudo dpkg -i nginx_1.18.0-1~focal_amd64.deb
    npacking nginx (1.18.0-1~focal) ...
    Setting up nginx (1.18.0-1~focal) ...
    Created symlink /etc/systemd/system/multi-user.target.wants/nginx.service → /lib/systemd/system/nginx.service.
    Processing triggers for systemd (245.4-4ubuntu3.2) ...
    Processing triggers for man-db (2.9.1-1) ...

Удаление nginx

$ sudo dpkg --purge nginx nginx-plugins
    (Reading database ... 190023 files and directories currently installed.)
    Removing nginx (1.18.0-1~focal) ...
    Purging configuration files for nginx (1.18.0-1~focal) ...
    dpkg: warning: ignoring request to remove nginx-plugins which isn't installed
    Processing triggers for man-db (2.9.1-1) ...
    Processing triggers for systemd (245.4-4ubuntu3.2) ...



